              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Two different detector system Plastic Ball and",
                "the SALAD (Small-Angle Large-Acceptance Detector) were",
                "used.",
                " Plastic Ball consists of 340 dE-E particle identifying",
                "detector modules. Each dE counter is a 4-mm thick",
                "CaF(2) crystal, the E counter is a 35.6-cm thick",
                "plastic scintillator.",
                "The SALAD consists of a dE plane of 24 thin",
                "scintillators and an E plane of 24 thick scintillators.",
                "Angular ranges:",
                "5 - 32 degrees for SALAD;",
                "91-160 degrees for Plastic Ball."
              ]
